# Voice Mapping Examples:
# pam_female_professional - Professional mature female voice (Edge: JennyNeural, Coqui: p267)
# pam_female_friendly - Warm, friendly female voice (Edge: AriaNeural, Coqui: p225)
# pam_male_professional - Authoritative professional male voice (Edge: DavisNeural, Coqui: p228)
# pam_travel_guide - Energetic voice for travel content (Edge: SaraNeural, Coqui: p229)
# pam_default - Default PAM voice with intelligent fallbacks

